# Risk Disclosure

## Overview

PNJC is a decentralized experimental ecosystem token.

---

## Market Risk

- Token price is determined by market supply and demand
- No guaranteed returns exist
- Liquidity may be limited at early stages

---

## Technical Risk

- Smart contracts may contain undiscovered vulnerabilities
- DeFi protocols are experimental by nature

---

## Liquidity Risk

- Early liquidity pools may experience high volatility
- Impermanent loss may occur for liquidity providers

---

## Participation Notice

Users participate in PNJC ecosystem at their own discretion and risk.
